story**
Once upon a time in a forest,tere lived a monkey who resided on a berry tree,which was on the banks of a river .In the same foest there lived a crocodile and his Wife
one day the crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree.
Monkey offered him fruits,the crocodile came back next day for more fruits.the
crocodile and monkey beacme friendk.
